Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这是昨天森田留下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田学长 我还以为他印下阿久的脚印要干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何止这个 之前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐到这个上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不－要－  讨－厌－啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修救救我～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近森田老是执拗地追着她跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这全是为了他的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田那家伙总是隔两三天就拿出新作来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这件作品还真出色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不把这种本事用在课题上呢 森田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 阿久怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 她可是完全怕了森田啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在躲在里面对着作品发泄压力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作品？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没见过阿久的作品 能看一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要集中注意力 你们小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底在做什么东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:02:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级大作～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 她注意力很集中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦做起来连一口水都不喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要装饰在这次横滨新开的美术馆的大厅中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个熟人从阿久高一的时候起就很欣赏她 是个画廊的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他捎话给我说“一定要让阿久来做”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们吃惊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我每次看到阿久的作品都感到震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论什么东西 都好像马上就要动起来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟 花 人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那个画廊老板也经常说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望自己能当一回阿久 用阿久的眼睛来看世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知看到的世界是什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能令别人有那样的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是所谓的才能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 就算是阿久的脚印也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我也吃了一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点受打击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽是想有所作为才上了美大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但将来要在哪儿工作 想做什么之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还完全没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 看到阿久之后我有点着急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 森田学长虽然经常乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他好像也在某地干着很了不得的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不了解那人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 真山学长毕业之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很快会被你打工的那个店铺设计事务所聘请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说理花小姐那儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我还不确定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大婶 我再要一片炸什锦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.66,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,（译注：炸什锦是天敷罗的一种）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才上2年级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急 什么都尝试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是只有一点兴趣 试着慢慢开始着手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能学会的事有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周左右咱们大张旗鼓地 在室外来一个铁板烧派对怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把阿久和公寓的人都叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊 就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荞麦面要糊掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把汤汁甩得到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 贴着自己想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉拖 手提包 连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.44,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,（译注：凉拖是一种鞋后跟无鞋带的凉鞋款式）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇好贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩的用品有这么贵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想买吗？可是 价钱很贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深受打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 正因为买不起才贴出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是旭堂书店的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科 科洛朴克尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在互联网上看到了和你很像的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互联网？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个网站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn汉仪丫丫体简}{\pos(525,280)}{\frz-23}{\fs30}{\1c&H6F79FB&}{\2a&H32&\2c&H4C4C4C&}{\b1}\N终\N于\N发\N现\N!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（呀啊啊啊啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是森田君！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是前些天的蘑菇椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这是前天的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 森田做得也太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画面上到处点缀着广告链接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点击一次能得到多少钱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直就是陷阱 想要进入下一页了结果一点击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有50%都是商业广告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？一天就达到10万HIT！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因为这是深受FANS欢迎的网站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更新很频繁 隐藏房间也在逐渐增多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿久你振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的守护灵是盖茨大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.45,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,（译注：比尔 盖茨 美国微软公司创始人）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 那个人还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该说“真不愧是他”呢还是别的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是说他不论摔得有多惨也要捞一把钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 森田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足型的纸镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 你被她讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 请务必把那个卖给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 足型纸镇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼疼疼疼疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有疼的地方请去保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这是 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 森田 咱们要开一个铁板烧派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和花本老师 阿久 以及公寓的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从今晚开始出去赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要走几天呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概要一周吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么一周后见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必要回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他不回来 我要你请我吃A套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫山田亚由美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花本叶久美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田学长真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田真的说要一周吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是第9天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是工作延长了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧 咱们来开派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久也会来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是等他吧 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田怎么说也是容易寂寞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他看上去也很期待 我怕他会难受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以咱们等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田容易寂寞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非竹本竟然像大人一样成熟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎…光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客…客人 你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 把能放进这只脚的鞋子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎那个…3万2千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要如何付款呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我赶时间 请就那样卖给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来她做得还不错 算我没白介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我们大学收了一个我亲戚的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花本叶久美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是用那种材料做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有白叫她来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能干好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢 原田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田学长什么时候才能回来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了别再等了 咱们吃肉吧吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路里不足也很严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本 铁板烧派对我有点迟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 学长 你给我们买回来肉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉一公斤680日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长你真有毅力啊（一直等到减价时才买）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大家一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非他们之间建立了某种信赖关系！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她相当讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是凉拖！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是粉色的亮晶晶的凉拖！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可～爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开～心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森森森田！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿修 阿修 阿久收到了凉拖！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我先回公寓让学长在床上睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他脸色有些差 而且也许睡48小时也起不来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长 铁板烧派对等森田醒来后再开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本 你真是个好人呐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明以前吃了他那么多苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我情不自禁地想起了老家的忠犬SABU
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉色的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 是森田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那么令人怀念的凉鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉色的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在哪里找到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉色的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我上大学的时候 美国女孩穿的就是这个吗？那种款式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉色的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那双凉拖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田 那个到底花了多少钱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁～万岁～万岁～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好～重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至少也该把肉放到讨论室的冰箱里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 阿久真的很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定也会原谅那个主页的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得她穿那双凉鞋很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 她是真的 非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？为什么我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为什么 胃这么疼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我吃了什么奇怪的东西了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一停下来磨磨蹭蹭 就越来越重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田突然变重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是“子泣爷爷”？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.20,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,（译注：子泣爷爷是德岛县山里的妖怪 会发出小孩的哭声 附在人的身上会像石头一样重）
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 那是两段单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:17.75,song,NTP,0,0,0,,もしも君がいなくなってしまったら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:17.75,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:29.15,song,NTP,0,0,0,,例えばネコやイモムシになってしまったら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:29.15,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说你变成了猫或毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.64,song,NTP,0,0,0,,メソメソと泣くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.64,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,我会抽泣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:43.56,song,NTP,0,0,0,,でもそのうち都合のいいネタにしてしまうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:43.56,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过到时说不定还会成为合适的题材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:49.63,song,NTP,0,0,0,,ねぇだから今日はそういつもより
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:49.63,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 所以今天就比平常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.34,song,NTP,0,0,0,,長い電話をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.34,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,打更久的电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:16:00.03,song,NTP,0,0,0,,なんとなく君に後ろめたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:16:00.03,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有些亏欠你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:05.47,song,NTP,0,0,0,,やさしく振舞っておこう…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:05.47,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔地行动吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:20.61,song,NTP,0,0,0,,もしも君と友達になっていたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:20.61,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和你成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:31.01,song,NTP,0,0,0,,知ったふうな顔で助言してくれたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:31.01,song2,NTP,0,0,0,,若你故作明白地劝告我
